-- Insurance Rates Rose 3% in 1H 2012, Lloyd’s of London CEO Says
-- B y   K e v i n   C r o w l e y
-- 2012-09-26T11:50:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-26/insurance-rates-rose-3-in-1h-2012-lloyd-s-of-london-ceo-says.html
Premium rates need to rise from
current levels to maintain profitability, Lloyd’s CEO Richard
Ward says on Bloomberg Television.
* Premium rates in casualty and aviation insurance are at low
levels meaning insurers are only making “marginal” profits in
those classes: Ward
* Insurers need to maintain price “discipline": Ward  To contact the reporter on this story:
